description: This file defines a Java interface called RequestEvent, which is intended for events that originate from server requests and include a request ID. It contains a single method getRequestId() that returns a long value representing the request identifier.

classes.name: RequestEvent
classes.description: An interface for events that stem from a server request and contain the requestId.

methods.name: getRequestId
methods.description: Returns the requestId that caused the operation and ultimately generated this event.
